{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-class-declarations-with-inline-styles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Pregazi Deklaracije Klase Inline Stilovima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dakle, potvrdili smo da id deklaracije pregaze deklaracije klase, bez obzira gde su deklarisane u CSS-u vaseg <code>style</code> elementa.</p>\n<p>Postoji jos nacina za pregazivanje CSS-a. Secate li se inline stilova?</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf06756","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristite inline stil da pokusate da nas <code>h1</code> element bude beo. Podsetnik, inline stil izgleda ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;h1 style=\"color: green;\">\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ostavite klase <code>blue-text</code> i <code>pink-text</code> na svom <code>h1</code> elementu.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cGJDRha","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18252,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-class-declarations-with-inline-styles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  body {\n    background-color: black;\n    font-family: monospace;\n    color: green;\n  }\n  #orange-text {\n    color: orange;\n  }\n  .pink-text {\n    color: pink;\n  }\n  .blue-text {\n    color: blue;\n  }\n</style>\n<h1 id=\"orange-text\" class=\"pink-text blue-text\">Hello World!</h1>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>pink-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h1').classList.contains('pink-text'));"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>blue-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('h1').classList.contains('blue-text'));"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima id <code>orange-text</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(document.querySelector('h1').getAttribute('id'), 'orange-text');"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da ima inline stil.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('h1[style]'));"},{"text":"<p>Vas <code>h1</code> element treba da bude bele boje.</p>","testString":"const h1Element = document.querySelector('h1');\nconst color = window.getComputedStyle(h1Element)['color']; \nassert.strictEqual(color, 'rgb(255, 255, 255)');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#basic-css","dashedName":"override-class-declarations-with-inline-styles","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-css","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-all-other-styles-by-using-important","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-class-declarations-by-styling-id-attributes","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aedf06756","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>@media (max-width: 350px) {:root {--penguin-size: 200px; --penguin-skin: black;}}</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/override-class-declarations-with-inline-styles"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}